# Organism solver file, specifying type of numerical solver
# and simulation time, used for
#
# 'Control of plant organogenesis by adaxial-abaxial boundaries'
#
# Author: Andre Larsson
# Contact: Henrik Jonsson (henrik.jonsson@slcu.cam.ac.uk)
#

RK5Adaptive   # solver type
0 50000      # start time, end time
2 100	      # output format, number of data points
0.05 1e-5     # max step, error tolerance
